#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.106"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.106:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.106:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga "
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.106:0.3"
msgid "106. Nijjarasutta "
msgstr "106. Wearing Away "

# NOTE: BB has “cases”, but the text, which echoes the phrasing of the previous suttas, is talking about causes for wearing away, so “grounds” seems better.sc1pts-vp-pli5.215
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
msgctxt "an10.106:0.4"
msgid "“Dasayimāni, bhikkhave, nijjaravatthūni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these ten grounds for wearing away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:0.5"
msgid "Katamāni dasa? "
msgstr "What ten? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.106:0.6"
msgid "Sammādiṭṭhikassa, bhikkhave, micchādiṭṭhi nijjiṇṇā hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right view, wrong view is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:0.7"
msgid "ye ca micchādiṭṭhipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong view are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:0.8"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (1) "
msgstr "And because of right view, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.106:2.1"
msgid "Sammāsaṅkappassa, bhikkhave, micchāsaṅkappo nijjiṇṇo hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right thought, wrong thought is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:2.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāsaṅkappapaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong thought are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:2.3"
msgid "sammāsaṅkappapaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (2) "
msgstr "And because of right thought, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.106:3.1"
msgid "Sammāvācassa, bhikkhave, micchāvācā nijjiṇṇā hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right speech, wrong speech is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:3.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāvācāpaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong speech are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:3.3"
msgid "sammāvācāpaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (3) "
msgstr "And because of right speech, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.106:4.1"
msgid "Sammākammantassa, bhikkhave, micchākammanto nijjiṇṇo hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right action, wrong action is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:4.2"
msgid "ye ca micchākammantapaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong action are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:4.3"
msgid "sammākammantapaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (4) "
msgstr "And because of right action, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.106:5.1"
msgid "Sammāājīvassa, bhikkhave, micchāājīvo nijjiṇṇo hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right livelihood, wrong livelihood is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:5.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāājīvapaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong livelihood are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:5.3"
msgid "sammāājīvapaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (5) "
msgstr "And because of right livelihood, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.106:6.1"
msgid "Sammāvāyāmassa, bhikkhave, micchāvāyāmo nijjiṇṇo hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right effort, wrong effort is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:6.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāvāyāmapaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong effort are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:6.3"
msgid "sammāvāyāmapaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (6) "
msgstr "And because of right effort, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.106:7.1"
msgid "Sammāsatissa, bhikkhave, micchāsati nijjiṇṇā hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right mindfulness, wrong mindfulness is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:7.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāsatipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong mindfulness are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:7.3"
msgid "sammāsatipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (7) "
msgstr "And because of right mindfulness, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.216, sc8
msgctxt "an10.106:8.1"
msgid "Sammāsamādhissa, bhikkhave, micchāsamādhi nijjiṇṇo hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right immersion, wrong immersion is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:8.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāsamādhipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong immersion are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:8.3"
msgid "sammāsamādhipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (8) "
msgstr "And because of right immersion, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an10.106:9.1"
msgid "Sammāñāṇissa, bhikkhave, micchāñāṇaṃ nijjiṇṇaṃ hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right knowledge, wrong knowledge is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:9.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāñāṇapaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong knowledge are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:9.3"
msgid "sammāñāṇapaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (9) "
msgstr "And because of right knowledge, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.106:10.1"
msgid "Sammāvimuttissa, bhikkhave, micchāvimutti nijjiṇṇā hoti; "
msgstr "For one of right freedom, wrong freedom is worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:10.2"
msgid "ye ca micchāvimuttipaccayā aneke pāpakā akusalā dhammā sambhavanti te cassa nijjiṇṇā honti; "
msgstr "And the many bad, unskillful qualities that arise because of wrong freedom are worn away. "

msgctxt "an10.106:10.3"
msgid "sammāvimuttipaccayā ca aneke kusalā dhammā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti. (10) "
msgstr "And because of right freedom, many skillful qualities are fully developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an10.106:11.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, dasa nijjaravatthūnī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the ten grounds for wearing away.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.106:11.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
